//eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/issue/18804/comment/39947","id":"39947","author":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=noirin","name":"noirin","key":"noirin","accountId":"557058:5be58e21-7229-47a3-a96a-befe39338f69","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/8097d864e3191f12bf80a64ae723fe42?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FownerId%3Dnoirin%26avatarId%3D12600%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/8097d864e3191f12bf80a64ae723fe42?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26ownerId%3Dnoirin%26avatarId%3D12600%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/8097d864e3191f12bf80a64ae723fe42?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26ownerId%3Dnoirin%26avatarId%3D12600%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","32x32":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/8097d864e3191f12bf80a64ae723fe42?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26ownerId%3Dnoirin%26avatarId%3D12600%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayName":"Nóirín Plunkett","active":false,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"body":"The reference architecture docs have moved to https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/wiki/display/EUCA/Eucalyptus+Reference+Architectures\r\n\r\nThere were a few things I couldn't get to in the limited time\r\navailable for review: please understand that these suggestions are ideals, and\r\nI'd much rather see us publish something that's 90% right away, rather\r\nthan waiting until there's time to make it perfect.\r\n\r\n- Single sourcing more of the content: it's great to see that there's\r\nsome common stuff that's pulled in from one place, but there's also\r\nquite a bit of common information that is just copy-pasted in each\r\ndoc. That's a pain for consistency and making sure that bugs found in\r\none doc are corrected wherever else they also appear.\r\n\r\n- Simple English: these documents are written at a 12th Grade reading\r\nlevel. That's *high*. Many legal documents in the US are required (by\r\nlaw!) to be no more than a 9th Grade reading level. Technical\r\ndocumentation should ideally be around a 6th Grade level. This helps\r\nbusy admins and architects, but also makes life easier for anyone\r\nwho's using Google Translate or similar to read our documentation :-)\r\nIt's perhaps less important for the reference architecture than for\r\nsome of our stuff, but let's talk before you create the next set of\r\ndocs about how we can bring down the reading level.\r\n\r\n- Configuration options: I was surprised at how relatively few\r\nsuggestions we made here. Perhaps that's all we can do in a reference\r\narchitecture, since individual circumstances vary so widely, but it\r\nwould be great to get some more information on how to tune some of the\r\nmore common configuration options.\r\n","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=noirin","name":"noirin","key":"noirin","accountId":"557058:5be58e21-7229-47a3-a96a-befe39338f69","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/8097d864e3191f12bf80a64ae723fe42?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FownerId%3Dnoirin%26avatarId%3D12600%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/8097d864e3191f12bf80a64ae723fe42?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26ownerId%3Dnoirin%26avatarId%3D12600%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/8097d864e3191f12bf80a64ae723fe42?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26ownerId%3Dnoirin%26avatarId%3D12600%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","32x32":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/8097d864e3191f12bf80a64ae723fe42?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26ownerId%3Dnoirin%26avatarId%3D12600%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayName":"Nóirín Plunkett","active":false,"timeZone":"America/Los_Angeles"},"created":"2013-02-20T11:23:35.867-0600","updated":"2013-02-20T11:23:35.867-0600"},{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/issue/18804/comment/98507","id":"98507","author":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=lbiasi","name":"lbiasi","key":"lbiasi","accountId":"557058:daaebf52-3713-4e4f-a29b-79f55aed32c9","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/3d92822583af436915b8264dbff0d30a?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FownerId%3Dlbiasi%26avatarId%3D15002%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/3d92822583af436915b8264dbff0d30a?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26ownerId%3Dlbiasi%26avatarId%3D15002%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/3d92822583af436915b8264dbff0d30a?s=16&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dxsmall%26ownerId%3Dlbiasi%26avatarId%3D15002%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","32x32":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/3d92822583af436915b8264dbff0d30a?s=32&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dmedium%26ownerId%3Dlbiasi%26avatarId%3D15002%26noRedirect%3Dtrue"},"displayName":"Leslie Biasi","active":false,"timeZone":"US/Central"},"body":"moving to closed","updateAuthor":{"self":"https://eucalyptus.atlassian.net/rest/api/2/user?username=lbiasi","name":"lbiasi","key":"lbiasi","accountId":"557058:daaebf52-3713-4e4f-a29b-79f55aed32c9","avatarUrls":{"48x48":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/3d92822583af436915b8264dbff0d30a?s=48&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3FownerId%3Dlbiasi%26avatarId%3D15002%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","24x24":"https://avatar-cdn.atlassian.com/3d92822583af436915b8264dbff0d30a?s=24&d=https%3A%2F%2Feucalyptus.atlassian.net%2Fsecure%2Fuseravatar%3Fsize%3Dsmall%26ownerId%3Dlbiasi%26avatarId%3D15002%26noRedirect%3Dtrue","16x16":"https://